originalSql:
WITH UserBadgeCounts AS (
    SELECT 
        u.Id AS UserId,
        u.DisplayName,
        COUNT(b.Id) AS BadgeCount,
        SUM(CASE WHEN b.Class = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GoldCount,
        SUM(CASE WHEN b.Class = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS SilverCount,
        SUM(CASE WHEN b.Class = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS BronzeCount
    FROM Users u
    LEFT JOIN Badges b ON u.Id = b.UserId
    GROUP BY u.Id, u.DisplayName
),
PostStats AS (
    SELECT 
        p.OwnerUserId,
        COUNT(p.Id) AS TotalPosts,
        COUNT(CASE WHEN p.PostTypeId = 1 THEN 1 END) AS QuestionCount,
        COUNT(CASE WHEN p.PostTypeId = 2 THEN 1 END) AS AnswerCount,
        SUM(p.Score) AS TotalScore
    FROM Posts p
    GROUP BY p.OwnerUserId
),
CombinedStats AS (
    SELECT 
        u.Id AS UserId,
        u.DisplayName,
        u.Reputation,
        COALESCE(ub.BadgeCount, 0) AS BadgeCount,
        COALESCE(ub.GoldCount, 0) AS GoldCount,
        COALESCE(ub.SilverCount, 0) AS SilverCount,
        COALESCE(ub.BronzeCount, 0) AS BronzeCount,
        COALESCE(ps.TotalPosts, 0) AS TotalPosts,
        COALESCE(ps.QuestionCount, 0) AS QuestionCount,
        COALESCE(ps.AnswerCount, 0) AS AnswerCount,
        COALESCE(ps.TotalScore, 0) AS TotalScore
    FROM Users u
    LEFT JOIN UserBadgeCounts ub ON u.Id = ub.UserId
    LEFT JOIN PostStats ps ON u.Id = ps.OwnerUserId
)
SELECT 
    UserId,
    DisplayName,
    Reputation,
    BadgeCount,
    GoldCount,
    SilverCount,
    BronzeCount,
    TotalPosts,
    QuestionCount,
    AnswerCount,
    TotalScore
FROM CombinedStats
WHERE TotalPosts > 0
ORDER BY TotalScore DESC, Reputation DESC
LIMIT 10

FROM (SELECT "Users"."Id" AS "USERID", "Users"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", "Users"."Reputation" AS "REPUTATION", CASE WHEN "t4"."BADGECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."BADGECOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "BADGECOUNT", CASE WHEN "t4"."GOLDCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."GOLDCOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "GOLDCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t4"."SILVERCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."SILVERCOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "SILVERCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t4"."BRONZECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."BRONZECOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "BRONZECOUNT", CASE WHEN "s1"."TOTALPOSTS" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("s1"."TOTALPOSTS" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "TOTALPOSTS", CASE WHEN "s1"."QUESTIONCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("s1"."QUESTIONCOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "QUESTIONCOUNT", CASE WHEN "s1"."ANSWERCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("s1"."ANSWERCOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "ANSWERCOUNT", CASE WHEN "s1"."TOTALSCORE" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("s1"."TOTALSCORE" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "TOTALSCORE"
FROM "Users"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT MIN("Users0"."Id") AS "USERID", "Users0"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", COUNT("Badges"."Id") AS "BADGECOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "GOLDCOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "SILVERCOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "BRONZECOUNT"
FROM "Users" AS "Users0"
LEFT JOIN "Badges" ON "Users0"."Id" = "Badges"."UserId"
GROUP BY "Users0"."Id", "Users0"."DisplayName") AS "t4" ON "Users"."Id" = "t4"."USERID"
LEFT JOIN "s1" ON "Users"."Id" = "s1"."OWNERUSERID") AS "t5"
WHERE "t5"."TOTALPOSTS" > 0
ORDER BY "TOTALSCORE" DESC NULLS FIRST, "REPUTATION" DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 10

FROM "Users"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT MIN("Users0"."Id") AS "USERID", "Users0"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", COUNT("Badges"."Id") AS "BADGECOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "GOLDCOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "SILVERCOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "BRONZECOUNT"
